OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPost Office scandal:       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGovernment to foot bill for
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpostmasters' compensation  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has agreed to foot the  
OL,6, bill for the compensation of former    
OL,7, Post Office workers who were falsely   
OL,8, convicted of theft in the long-running 
OL,9, Horizon saga.                          
OL,11,FThe Post Office has said it is unable  
OL,12,Fto cover the payments for the          
OL,13,Fexonerated individuals.                
OL,15,FAs the Post Office's only shareholder, 
OL,16,Fthe government has confirmed in a      
OL,17,Fstatement that it will pay.            
OL,19,FSo far, 72 postmasters' convictions    
OL,20,Fhave been quashed.                     
